parameters:
Memimi: *pant* *pant*... Somehow, my body feels hot... I
must calm down... My head's getting hazy... Ahh...

Bystander: Ah, it's Shark Duke... Now that I think about it,
his true identity is the student council president from that
school. What's he doing in a swimsuit... No, wait, what?!
Underwear...?

Male Student: Ah, the president... No, is that the Shark
Duke's hat...? In underwear at the school... That's
amazing...

Memimi: Haah, so noisy... So many men... It's making me
horny...
Male Student: Pre-president!? What's going... Uwaaaah!!!

Memimi: Be quiet, you commoners!! Now, Shark Duke here will
take away your chastity!! Mwahaha... Strip off your clothes!
Line up!!
Bystander: Why, why is this happening...?

Classmate: President, what happened to you!! Ugh, you smell
like alcohol... Are you drunk...?

Student Council Vice President: It's not good to commit acts
of violence on the school grounds, President!! Please come
back to your senses quickly!!
Principal: Mr. Samayama, this is a serious problem...?

Memimi: Did the others run away~... Ufufu, well, having just
these is enough... I can pick and choose... Ufufu...

The curtain rises on a dreadful scene of violation by
Memimi, who has gone into a rampage...
